des: Fueling Life is a podcast brought to you by — and all about — Diffusion Pharmaceuticals, an innovative biopharmaceutical company developing novel therapies that enhance the body’s ability to deliver oxygen where it is needed most. This podcast will explore the science and ongoing studies of trans sodium crocetinate (TSC), our first-in-class, small molecule therapeutic that enhances the diffusion of oxygen to hypoxic tissues.
